<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="behind-prep">behind <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɪ'haɪnd/    美 /bɪ'haɪnd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在…后面；支持：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Close the door of fear behind you, and you will see the door of faith open before you. 
把恐惧之门关在你的身后，你将会看见信念之门在你面前打开。</p><footer>2012 湖南</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We’re always behind you.
我们永远支持你。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>落后于；不如：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>behind the times 
落后于时代</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Japan is behind the United States in e-business. 
在电子商务方面日本不如美国。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>(时间、进度等) 迟于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>New York is 12 hours behind Beijing. 
纽约时间比北京晚12个小时。</p></div></div>